## Overview
Isle of Berk Nova Dragon Variants is a collection of 13 unique re-skinned variants.

## Important
1. The **Isle of Berk Mod**, **Isle of Berk Variant Loader Mod** and **Archipelago Additions Mod**  is required for this to work.

## Recommended Modpack(s) 
- [**Scales and Skies**](https://modrinth.com/modpack/scales-and-skies)
- [**Claws of Berk**](https://modrinth.com/modpack/new-berks-dawn)
- [**Across the Archipelago**](https://modrinth.com/modpack/across-the-archipelago)

## Spawn Commands - (Reference number with Gallery)
```
1 - /summon isleofberk:night_fury ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:aurorae}
2 - /summon isleofberk:monstrous_nightmare ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:cataclysm}
3 - /summon isleofberk:night_fury ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:celestial}
4 - /summon isleofberk:deadly_nadder ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:tropical_reef}
5 - /summon isleofberk:gronckle ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:coral_splash}
6 - /summon isleofberk:gronckle ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:seashell_splash}
7 - /summon isleofberk:light_fury ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:astrella}
8 - /summon isleofberk:light_fury ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:floral_petal}
9 - /summon isleofberk:light_fury ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:luminara}
10 - /summon isleofberk:night_fury ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:aetherion}
11 - /summon isleofberk:night_fury ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:serenyx}
12 - /summon isleofberk:night_fury ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:tide_runner}
13 - /summon isleofberk:triple_stryke ~ ~ ~ {VariantName:singularity}
```
